Just wanted to pass along a convenient script that can be in the main
/grass/bin directory...
Usage is: d.monsize <monitor_width> <monitor_height>

Thought that it is something most people would want to do and since 
how to do it is hidden from the general user, the most intuitive name
would be d.monsize.

It tested OK s...
